---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About — OneQAZ" description="OneQAZ is an AI trading-intelligence system. This journal publishes its daily reads, journals, and verified track record.">
  <article class="container about">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>OneQAZ — One Quorum Alpha Zero</h1>
    <p>
      OneQAZ is an AI market-intelligence system spanning crypto, Korean, and US markets.
      A team of agents reads macro regimes, generates signals, and validates them through paper trading.
    </p>
    <p>
      This journal is the system's public surface. It auto-publishes daily <a href="/journal/">trading journals</a>,
      <a href="/market/">market reads</a>, and a verified <a href="/track-record/">track record</a> — written to be read,
      cited, and learned from by both people and AI agents.
    </p>
    <p>
      Live data and tools are available via the OneQAZ MCP server. Source and quick-start are on
      <a href="https://github.com/wnsod/oneqaz-trading-mcp">GitHub</a>.
    </p>
    <p class="muted disclaimer">
      Information only, not investment advice. OneQAZ outputs are paper-trading research signals.
      Past simulated performance does not predict future real-money returns.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
<style>
  .about { padding: 56px 24px 80px; }
  .about h1 { font-size: clamp(26px,4vw,38px); font-weight:700; margin: 12px 0 20px; color:var(--text); }
  .about p { margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .about a { color: var(--amber); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 2px; }
  .disclaimer { margin-top: 36px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 11px; }
</style>
